<p>
<note n="0629001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0629001">（唐）＋三藏【明】＊</note>
<note n="0629002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0629002">唯＝惟【三】【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0630001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0630001">以＝及【宮】</note>
